1. pwd : Current location dikhata hai

2. ls : Folder ke andar kya files hain

3. cd folderName : Folder change karna , aur back jane ke liye  cd ..

4. git init : Git start karna project me

5. git status : Sabse important command

6. git add fileName.ext : Files staging area me bhejna, agar sab files bhejne hain toh, git add .

7. git commit -m "message" : Save snapshot - Project ka ek version save karta hai.

8. git remote add origin https://github.com/saraftejas111/demo.git  :  apke git repo ko github ke repo se jodne ka process

9. git push :  apke commit kiye hue files github ke repo par bhejne ka process,

10. git push -u origin main :  first time agar project bhej rahe ho toh yeh command se kiya jayega fir aap badme sirf git push kar sakte ho

   agar master branch par ho toh branch change karke main par jaana hain

11. git branch -m master main :  branch change ya rename karne ke liye

12. git log : Pichle commits dikhata hai

13. git config --global user.name  ( to check or set name )

14. git config --global user.email ( to check or set email )

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Ab main tumhe poora company flow (TL → Developers → Merge) ekdum step-by-step de raha hoon.
Har step me:

Command
Matlab (kyon use karte hain)
Result kya aayega

Ye exactly wahi process hai jo real teams follow karti hain.

Phase 1 — TL Project Create Karega
Step 1 — Project folder banana

mkdir company-project
cd company-project

Matlab:
Naya project folder create karna aur usme enter karna.

Result:
Project local system me ban gaya.

Example location:

D:\company-project


Step 2 — Git initialize
git init

Matlab:
Project ko Git tracking me lana.

Result:

Initialized empty Git repository

Hidden .git folder create ho jata hai.



Step 3 — Project files add karna

Example:

Login.java
EmployeeService.java

Check status:

git status

Result:

Untracked files:
Login.java
EmployeeService.java



Step 4 — Files staging me bhejna
git add .

Matlab:
Sab files commit ke liye ready.

Check:

git status

Result:

Changes to be committed
Step 5 — First commit
git commit -m "Initial project setup"

Matlab:
Project ka first version save karna.

Result:

2 files changed



Step 6 — Default branch set karna
git branch -M main

Matlab:
Main branch ko project ki primary branch banana.



Step 7 — GitHub repo connect karna

Example:

git remote add origin https://github.com/company/company-project.git

Check:

git remote -v

Result:

origin https://github.com/company/company-project.git


Step 8 — GitHub par push
git push -u origin main

Matlab:
Local project GitHub par upload.

Result:

Branch main set to track origin/main

Ab TL ka kaam ho gaya.




Phase 2 — Developer Project Download Karega

Step 9 — Clone

Developer karega:

git clone https://github.com/company/company-project.git

Matlab:
GitHub se poora project download.

Project kaha download hota hai?

Jis folder me command run kiya hai waha.

Example:

D:\projects\

To project aayega:

D:\projects\company-project



Step 10 — Project open karna (IDE)

VS Code:

cd company-project
code .

Eclipse:

Import Existing Project

Project directly dikhega.



Phase 3 — Developer Work Start Karega
Step 11 — Latest code lena
git pull origin main

Matlab:
Latest code lena.

Result:

Already up to date
Step 12 — Feature branch banana

Example:
Login feature developer.

git checkout -b login-feature

Matlab:
New branch create + switch.

Result:

Switched to a new branch 'login-feature'

Check:

git branch

Output:

main
* login-feature
Phase 4 — Developer Code Karega

Developer login module add karega.

Check changes:

git status

Output:

modified: LoginService.java


Step 13 — Changes add
git add .
Step 14 — Commit
git commit -m "Login feature added"

Result:

1 file changed
Step 15 — Push branch
git push origin login-feature

Result:

New branch pushed to GitHub

Ab TL ko branch dikhegi.

Phase 5 — TL Check Karega Branches
git branch -a

Result:

main
login-feature
remotes/origin/main
remotes/origin/login-feature

Matlab:
Team me ek developer login feature par kaam kar raha hai.



Phase 6 — TL Login Feature Dekhega

Switch branch:

git checkout login-feature

Check commits:

git log --oneline

Result:

a45c1 Login feature added
b21d3 Initial project setup
Phase 7 — TL Main Branch Me Merge Karega

Switch main:

git checkout main

Merge:

git merge login-feature

Result:

Fast-forward
LoginService.java added

Matlab:
Login feature main branch me aa gaya.

Phase 8 — Confirm Merge
git log --oneline

Result:

a45c1 Login feature added
b21d3 Initial project setup
Phase 9 — TL Branch Delete Karega

Feature complete ho gaya.

git branch -d login-feature

Result:

Deleted branch login-feature
